+    """Classify at most ``limit`` raw gaps and return resumable progress.
+
+    The cursor and accumulated category counters are valid only while the caller's
+    source fingerprint remains unchanged. StatusSnapshotRegistry enforces that
+    invariant before supplying a previous value to the exact diagnostic collector.
+    """
